2018-08-22T03:18:38.000Z","msg":"一睇 GitHub 就知 Vue 不入流<br />\n<br />\nReact - ★ 109286<br />\nAngular - ★ 39717<br />\nVue - ★ 111560"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T11:12:07.000Z","msg":"如果睇埋每日增加人數, Angular係增長最高"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T08:42:55.000Z","msg":"我覺得咁低因為angularJS轉angular個期得罪太多人，同埋好多nodejs接收好多php難民但佢地又玩唔掂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T03:07:29.000Z","msg":"其實又唔算得罪<br />\nAngularJS經歷ES2015出場<br />\nJS ecosystem 生態大變革<br />\nAngularJS得2條路，小改定大改<br />\n然後React出現，追求致極Dom Rendering，將紅極一時既AngularJS 比下去<br />\nAngular大改路線已經決定<br />\n不過大改代價就係要投資更多時間<br />\n當ES2015成熟時，市佔已經畀其他能用ES2015的library/framework 搶了不少<br />\nBreaking Change 的代價不少<br />\n但Angular在這次大改上痛定思痛如何能避免下一次再次被ECMAScript改版玩殘<br />\nAngular現在用上了Typescript 同semver <br />\n還有同步在Dart上開發<br />\n盡力確保Angular不會經歷AngularJS 既失敗"},{"pid":"1e36b909b8024c9b1429a59ed02295b883d4d053","tid":787820,"uid":61249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T08:13:30.000Z","msg":"only redux-saga do testing right<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1a427dd1493b9a2714ba097b068a6a3eab32951","tid":787820,"uid":116953,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"81c3dc53fdec96dd81b0a96655d925cd56c67df9","tid":787820,"uid":18296,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62efa4503637cd893988a608343dbaec7f10085d","tid":787820,"uid":116953,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"31822e2fd7054e0c3d21ee0627bff27a2a389cda","tid":787820,"uid":148652,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T11:48:48.000Z","msg":"暫時仲未入流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T03:18:38.000Z","msg":"一睇 GitHub 就知 Vue 不入流<br />\n<br />\nReact - ★ 109286<br />\nAngular - ★ 39717<br />\nVue - ★ 111560"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T08:02:42.000Z","msg":"大陸嘢通常都成炸蝗star,  多star ! == 多人用<br />\napache server都係得幾千粒star喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgm